---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Container } from '../../components/layout/Container';
import { Section } from '../../components/layout/Section';
import { Heading } from '../../components/ui/Heading';
import { Badge } from '../../components/ui/Badge';
import { CTASection } from '../../components/sections/CTASection';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Case Study: 312% ROAS Increase for Furniture Retailer - ProfitSEM"
  description="How we helped a premium furniture retailer increase ROAS from 1.8x to 5.6x in just 60 days."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <Section background="gradient" spacing="lg">
    <Container size="lg">
      <div class="text-center text-white mb-8">
        <Badge variant="success" size="md" className="mb-4 bg-white/20 text-white">
          E-commerce Case Study
        </Badge>
        <Heading as="h1" size="5xl" className="mb-4">
          312% ROAS Increase in 60 Days
        </Heading>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100">
          How we transformed a struggling furniture retailer's Google Ads into a profit machine
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">5.6x</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-blue-100">Final ROAS</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-blue-200 mt-1">From 1.8x</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">$186K</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-blue-100">Monthly Revenue</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-blue-200 mt-1">From $45K</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">-69%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-blue-100">CPA Reduction</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-blue-200 mt-1">$78 to $24</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur border border-white/20 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">60</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-blue-100">Days to Results</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-blue-200 mt-1">Under 90-day goal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- Background -->
  <Section background="white" spacing="lg">
    <Container size="lg">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
          <div>
            <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4">
              The Challenge
            </Heading>
            <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 space-y-4">
              <p>
                A premium furniture retailer came to us frustrated and ready to quit Google Ads entirely.
                Despite spending $42,000/month on Google Shopping and Search campaigns, they were barely
                breaking even with a ROAS of just 1.8x.
              </p>
              <p>
                Their previous agency had focused on "maximizing traffic" and "increasing impressions,"
                but the business wasn't growing. They were burning through budget on low-intent searches
                and getting clicks from people who had no intention of buying $3,000 sofas.
              </p>
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">
                The owner's words: "We're spending more on ads than we're making in profit. Something needs to change or we're done with Google Ads."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4">
              What We Found
            </Heading>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-red-900 mb-1">Wasted Budget on Low-Intent Keywords</p>
                  <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">37% of spend going to broad match keywords like "cheap furniture" and "furniture ideas" that never converted.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-red-900 mb-1">Poor Product Feed Quality</p>
                  <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">Shopping feed had generic titles, missing custom labels, and no negative keywords.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-red-900 mb-1">No Audience Segmentation</p>
                  <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">Treating first-time visitors the same as people who abandoned $5K+ carts.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-red-900 mb-1">Mobile Experience Disaster</p>
                  <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">57% of traffic was mobile but conversion rate was 0.3% (vs 2.1% desktop).</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4">
              Our Strategy
            </Heading>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                    1
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-1">Week 1-2: Profit Leak Elimination</p>
                  <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>Cut 340+ low-intent keywords (saved $15.4K/month)</li>
                    <li>Restructured campaigns by profit margin tiers</li>
                    <li>Added 800+ negative keywords</li>
                    <li>Implemented ROAS-based bid strategies</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                    2
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-1">Week 3-4: Shopping Feed Transformation</p>
                  <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>Rewrote all product titles for high-intent searches</li>
                    <li>Added custom labels for profit margin segmentation</li>
                    <li>Created separate campaigns for best sellers vs new inventory</li>
                    <li>Implemented dynamic remarketing</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                    3
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-1">Week 5-6: Audience Segmentation</p>
                  <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>Created high-value cart abandoner campaigns (avg cart: $4,200)</li>
                    <li>Built RLSA campaigns for past purchasers</li>
                    <li>Separated new vs returning visitor strategies</li>
                    <li>Implemented customer match for email list</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4 p-4 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">
                    4
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-1">Week 7-8: Mobile Optimization</p>
                  <ul class="text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>Worked with dev team on mobile landing page speed (4.2s → 1.8s)</li>
                    <li>Simplified mobile checkout (5 steps → 2 steps)</li>
                    <li>Mobile-specific ad copy testing</li>
                    <li>Adjusted bids based on device performance</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <Heading as="h2" size="3xl" className="mb-4">
              The Results
            </Heading>
            <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl p-6">
              <p class="text-lg text-green-900 mb-4">
                Within 60 days, the account was completely transformed:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span><strong>ROAS jumped from 1.8x to 5.6x</strong> (312% increase)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span><strong>Monthly revenue grew from $45K to $186K</strong> (313% increase)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span><strong>CPA dropped from $78 to $24</strong> (69% reduction)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span><strong>Conversion rate improved from 1.2% to 4.8%</strong> (300% increase)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span><strong>Mobile conversion rate: 0.3% → 3.2%</strong> (967% increase)</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-6 text-green-900 font-semibold italic">
                "Google Ads went from being a necessary evil to our #1 profit driver. We're now spending $65K/month and actually making money." - Business Owner
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Sidebar */}
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 sticky top-24">
            <Heading as="h3" size="lg" className="mb-4">
              Quick Facts
            </Heading>
            <dl class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <dt class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-1">Industry</dt>
                <dd class="font-semibold">E-commerce (Furniture)</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-1">Starting Ad Spend</dt>
                <dd class="font-semibold">$42,000/month</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-1">Timeline</dt>
                <dd class="font-semibold">60 days</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-1">Main Challenge</dt>
                <dd class="font-semibold">Low ROAS, wasted budget</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-1">Primary Tactics</dt>
                <dd class="font-semibold text-sm">
                  Keyword culling, feed optimization, audience segmentation, mobile fixes
                </dd>
              </div>
            </dl>

            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">Ready for similar results?</p>
              <a href="/free-analysis" class="block w-full text-center bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
                Get Free Analysis
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </Section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <CTASection client:visible />
</BaseLayout>
